==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ascomycota
<hw>Ascomycota</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a phylum of higher fungi,
coextensive with the class <class><er>Ascomycetes</er></class>. It
comprises Hemiascomycetes; Plectomycetes; Pyrenomycetes; Discomycetessac
fungi; in some classification systems it is considered a division of the
kingdom Fungi.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> subdivision Ascomycota, Ascomycotina, subdivision
Ascomycotina.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

